          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(center)">
                                        <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>
                                        <date>9 Sep 1846</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>My <addressee>Dr Mr. Leeser</addressee></p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">A great many of our children<lb/> have been
                                        neglected since I was forced from the Sunday<lb/> School,
                                        the parents declining to send them under the<lb/> existing
                                        regulations of the present <del>school</del>. I have<lb/>
                                        altho' urged, declined forming one for these who do not<lb/>
                                        receive the benefits, as I did not wish to come into<lb/>
                                        contact with the opposite party, finding however that
                                        the<lb/> children were really suffering, at the
                                        particular<lb/> solicitation of one of our most Respectable
                                        influential<lb/> members (who unhappily (was in
                                                  <placeName>Europe</placeName> when the
                                        differences<lb/> took place) having a large number of
                                        children, that really<lb/> require the advantage of
                                        Religious instruction–have<lb/> promised him to re-commence
                                        intend doing so as soon as<lb/> I shall receive from you the
                                        following books which I<lb/> require.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">36 Pyher[?] catechisms</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">36 cahiev[?]–24 Bible questions, by <persName>Miss
                                                  Peixotto</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">12 of your Catechisms; I beg that you will</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>send them with all haste. Wishing you many happy<lb/> holy days I
                                        am my Dr Sir Yours Truly</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">A Wolff</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p>7</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. Mr Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
